{"word":"ἰχθυάω","slug":"ἰχθυάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἰχθυάω</b></el> <el>(ἰχθυάω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἰχθύς'><el>ἰχθύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to fish, angle</i>, epic <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>ἰχθυάασκον</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to fish for</i>, epic 3rd sg. <el>ἰχθυάᾳ</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sport</i>, of fish, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}